###
### DemeterAI v2.0 - Product Controller HTTP Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000
### Controller: product_controller.py (C014-C020)
###

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiPrefix = /api/v1/products

###
### C014: GET - List product categories
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C015: GET - Get product families by category (Category ID: 1 - Cactus)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/categories/1/families
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C015: GET - Get product families by category (Category ID: 2 - Succulents)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/categories/2/families
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C016: GET - List all products (with pagination)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}?skip=0&limit=20
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C016: GET - List all products (default pagination)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C017: GET - Get product by ID (Product ID: 1)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C018: GET - Get products by family (Family ID: 1)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/families/1/products
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C019: GET - Get product sizes
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/sizes
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C020: GET - Get product states
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/states
Content-Type: application/json

###
### C020: GET - Get products by state (State: vegetative)
###
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/states/vegetative/products
Content-Type: application/json

###
### POST - Create product category
###
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Category",
  "description": "Test category for HTTP testing"
}

###
### POST - Create product family
###
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/families
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category_id": 1,
  "name": "Test Family",
  "description": "Test family for HTTP testing"
}

###
### POST - Create product
###
